{
  "description": "Pluggable suite registry consumed by run-qa.sh. Each suite maps to a build/test invocation. `component` ties results back to a catalog. `gate` suites must pass for the run to be releasable; `advisory` suites report without blocking. Adding a server later = one new entry, no orchestrator change.",
  "suites": [
